# AgToosa Update Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-update`, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Update.md` precisely.

**Contract:** Detect → Plan → Apply → Verify (ask-then-apply when drift is detected). Only `check` is read-only. Apply runs `agtoosa.sh --update` after explicit approval — never silent file sync.